  "prompt": "Which is the best immigration consultancy in India?",
  "response": "Determining the \"best\" immigration consultancy in India can be subjective and depends on various factors, including individual needs, the specific immigration program, location, and personal experiences. However, there are several well-known and reputable immigration consultants in India that have garnered positive reviews over the years. Some of them include:\n\n1. **Y-Axis**: One of the largest immigration consultancies, offering services for various countries.\n2. **Visas Avenue**: Known for its personalized services and comprehensive guidance on immigration processes.\n3. **Global Tree**: Offers immigration services along with education consultancy for studying abroad.\n4. **Abhinav Immigration**: A well-established consultancy with a focus on various immigration pathways.\n5. **WWICS (World Wide Immigration Consultancy Services)**: Offers a range of immigration services and has a global presence.\n\nWhen choosing an immigration consultancy, it's essential to conduct thorough research, read reviews, check their success rates, and consult with them directly to see if their services align with your needs. Always ensure that the consultancy is registered and has a good reputation to avoid scams or misinformation.",
